Finnish invoice LaTeX class
===========================

Goals
-----

Finnish invoice LaTeX class compliant with Federation of Finnish Financial Services SEPA invoice template [1]. 

Usage
-----

Fill in the macros in the PAYMENT DETAILS section. Fill in the products or services in the INVOICE section, which is just a LaTeX table. 

Select language by defining e.g. \def\finnish{}. Text strings are also marked for TRANSLATION in the preamble. 

References
----------

[1] https://www.fkl.fi/teemasivut/sepa/tekninen_dokumentaatio/Sivut/default.aspx

